Package: dlm
Type: Package
Title: Distributed Lag Models for Event Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Theodore", "Caputi", email = "tcaputi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements distributed lag models equivalent to event studies with
    binned endpoints, following Schmidheiny and Siegloch (2023, Journal of Applied
    Econometrics). Provides tools for estimation, visualization, and comparison
    with standard two-way fixed effects specifications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/tlcaputi/dlm
BugReports: https://github.com/tlcaputi/dlm/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
